talkEventOther30_3.value: Me siento tan feliz de que confíes más en ti, Nai.

talkEventOther30_4.name: Nai
talkEventOther30_4.value: .... Yo también seré feliz si se siente feliz señor.

talkEvent1_1.name: Yo
talkEvent1_1.value: Hola Nai, viviremos juntos de ahora en adelante.

talkEvent1_3.value: Nai pone sus ojos en blanco y se nota ansiosa, ella extiende su mano para agarrar su otro brazo de una manera algo extraña.

talkEvent1_4.value: Centro mi mirada sobre los movimientos de sus brazos blancos que están expuestos por la ropa sucia y gastada.

talkEvent1_6.value: Nai tenía moretones rosados ​​en todo el brazo, algunos de color rosa oscuro, otros de color rosa claro. Forman un marcado contraste con su piel blanca y se ven realmente dolorosos.

talkEvent1_7.name: Yo
talkEvent1_7.value: ¡¿Nai?! ¿Cómo obtuviste todos esos moretones en tu cuerpo?

talkEvent1_8.name: Nai
talkEvent1_8.value: .... Es ... Es ... porque Nai fue muy descuidada al tropezarse con algo ...

talkEvent1_9.name: Yo
talkEvent1_9.value: (¿Cómo alguien puede acabar con esos moretones por tropezar ... Pudo haber sido el resultado de haber sido golpeada por alguien?)

talkEvent1_10.name: Yo
talkEvent1_10.value: Bueno parece que en verdad no quisieras mencionarlo

talkEvent2_1.name: Yo
talkEvent2_1.value: ¿Tu nombre es Nai verdad? Es realmente un lindo nombre.

talkEvent2_3.name: Yo
talkEvent2_3.value: Tu mamá debio amarte mucho. Bueno de ahora en adelante te llamaré Nai, ¿de acuerdo?

talkEvent2_4.name: Nai
talkEvent2_4.value: .... Usted ... no debe pedir mi permiso para cosas ... como esa ...

talkEvent2_6.name: Nai
talkEvent2_6.value: .... Mi anterior dueño me enseñó ... que solo necesito obedecer las órdenes ... Dijo ... la basura no necesita tener ideas propias ...

talkEvent2_7.name: Yo
talkEvent2_7.value: (Parece que le han enseñado algunos conceptos muy extraños ... pobre niña).

talkEvent3_1.name: Yo
talkEvent3_1.value: Nai, ¿podrías decirme por qué te llamas basura?

talkEvent3_2.value: Nai me mira con una expresión perpleja, parpadeando sus inocentes y grandes ojos. Es comó si dijera que es extraño para mí hacer preguntas como esa.

talkEvent3_3.name: Nai
talkEvent3_3.value: No hay necesidad. Porque Nai es quien es ella.

talkEvent3_4.name: Yo
talkEvent3_4.value: Eso no es correcto Nai. Todos deben ser respetados y no eres ninguna basura. Lo que piensas me importa mucho.

talkEvent3_5.name: Nai
talkEvent3_5.value: ¿De Verdad? Pero solo soy un pedazo de basura ...

talkEvent3_6.name: Yo
talkEvent3_6.value: No, estas mal en absoluto. Eres una chica encantadora, no una basura de mierda. Eres un humano al igual que yo

talkEvent3_8.value: Se habla a sí misma con curiosidad y repite la palabra "humano" varias veces, pero aún así no la entiende.

talkEvent3_9.value: Ella baja la cabeza y acurruca su cuerpo para escapar del contacto visual conmigo.

talkEvent3_10.name: Yo
talkEvent3_10.value: (Ella es una chica con una historia que contar. ¡Necesito cambiar sus malos pensamientos!)

noFoodEvent_2.value: No hay dinero en casa ... no he comido nada en todo el día

dayEndEvent1_1.name: Yo
dayEndEvent1_1.value: Se está haciendo tarde. Creo que sera mejor acostarce a dormir.

dayBeginEvent1_1.name: Nai
dayBeginEvent1_1.value: Buenos días señor, ¿qué le gustaría hacer hoy?

talkEvent4_1.name: Yo
talkEvent4_1.value: Nai, ¿por qué te levantaste para hacer las tareas del hogar anoche?

talkEvent4_2.name: Nai
talkEvent4_2.value: Porque ... si no hago las tareas del hogar, seré basura ... "Y se desecha la basura inútil". No quiero ser desechada.

talkEvent4_3.name: Yo
talkEvent4_3.value: Nai, ¿por qué tienes esos pensamientos? En este mundo, una persona no tiene derecho de tirar a otra persona.

talkEvent4_4.name: Nai
talkEvent4_4.value: ... No ... Señor ... Incluso si cree que soy inútil y quiere tirarme, lo aceptaré ...

talkEvent4_5.name: Nai
talkEvent4_5.value: Pero me esforzaré por ser basura útil, hay algo que necesita el señor

talkEvent4_6.value: Estoy extremadamente sorprendido por las siniestras palabras que salen de la boca de Nai y sus comportamientos extraños anoche

talkEvent4_7.name: Yo
talkEvent4_7.value: (¿Por qué infierno debio haber pasado esta chica? No me lo quiero ni imaginar ...)

talkEvent4_8.name: Nai
talkEvent4_8.value: Señor ... trabajaré duro. Señor, por favor no me tire ...

talkEvent4_9.value: Nai está un poco nerviosa y parece tener miedo de que la tiren.

talkEvent4_10.name: Yo
talkEvent4_10.value: Nai ... por favor cálmate, no haré eso.

talkEvent4_11.name: Yo
talkEvent4_11.value: (Debe haber algo escondido dentro de su pasado. Mejor no continúe preguntando al respecto, para que no se vuelva más inestable emocionalmente.

talkEvent5_3.value: Cúando menciono a esa persona, Nai no pudo evitar mostrar expresiones de miedo.

talkEvent5_4.name: Nai
talkEvent5_4.value: Señor ... Nai definitivamente trabajará de la mañana a la noche y no será una chica perezosa.

talkEvent5_5.name: Nai
talkEvent5_5.value: Solo le pido que no me tire como basura

talkEvent5_6.name: Yo
talkEvent5_6.value: Nai, no eres basura y tampoco abandonaré

talkEvent5_7.name: Yo
talkEvent5_7.value: Realmente no necesitas trabajar así todo el tiempo. Descansa bien y vive una vida normal

talkEvent5_9.value: (La cara de Nai todavía parece asustada como si no creyera en mis palabras)

talkEvent6_1.name: Yo
talkEvent6_1.value: Nai. ¿Cómo era tu vida en el pasado? ¿Me podrías contar al respecto?

talkEvent6_2.name: Nai
talkEvent6_2.value: ...Tuve mucha suerte. Incluso para algo tan inútil como yo. Esa persona incluso estaba dispuesta a dejarme vivir ...

talkEvent6_5.name: Nai
talkEvent6_5.value: ... Él ... él es el dios de mi mundo.

talkEvent6_6.name: Nai
talkEvent6_6.value: Mientras obedeciera las órdenes, Dios nunca me abandonaría.

talkEvent6_7.name: Yo
talkEvent6_7.value: (¡Parece que el Dios mencionado por Nai es el que le dio ideas tan extrañas!)

talkEvent6_8.name: Yo
talkEvent6_8.value: Nai, no hay tal cosa como el Dios de este mundo. Tu eres el maestro de tu mundo.

talkEvent6_9.value: Nai me admira. Pero es evidente que sus ojos blancos detonen una enorme confusion.

talkEvent6_11.name: Yo
talkEvent6_11.value: Eso está bien, tómalo con calma. Te ayudare a entenderlo.

talkEvent7_3.value: Ella permanece en silencio por un momento y creo que no puede responder. No pude evitar sentirme decepcionado, pero de repente escucho una voz tan bajas como el zumbido de un mosquito.

talkEvent7_7.value: Nai de repente piensa en cosas horribles, retrocede y sacude la cabeza con preocupación. Ella se esconde y cubre su cabeza como si buscara protección.

talkEvent7_8.name: Nai
talkEvent7_8.value: .... No, en realidad yo ... ¡no me gustan los animales pequeños!

talkEvent7_9.name: Yo
talkEvent7_9.value: (Mirando las reacciones de Nai, siento que debe tener que ver con el "Dios" del que habló.

talkEvent8_1.name: Yo
talkEvent8_1.value: Nai, ¿alguien te a mencionado que eres bonita? Eres muy linda~

talkEvent8_2.name: Nai
talkEvent8_2.value: ¿Linda? ¿Cómo es que?... A mi odian mirarme ...

talkEvent8_3.value: La frustración y la vacilación de repente pasan por los ojos de Nai. Nai mira hacia abajo para jugar con sus manos. Después de un rato, ella habla con una debil voz ---

talkEvent8_4.name: Nai
talkEvent8_4.value: Esa persona dijo ... Yo era la más fea del mundo ...

talkEvent8_5.name: Yo
talkEvent8_5.value: Nunca he visto a una chica que sea más encantadora que tú. ¡Esa persona realmente habla idioteces! Realmente quisiera verlo y decircelo en la cara.

talkEvent8_6.name: Nai
talkEvent8_6.value: ... No ... no diga eso de esa persona ... Él me castigará ...

talkEvent8_8.value: La simple palabra parece darle un horrendo escalofrio a Nai. Se abraza y se esconde en el rincón oscuro. Ella deja de hablarme más.

talkEvent8_9.name: Yo
talkEvent8_9.value: (¿Cuál podria ser el castigo del que habla Nai?)

talkEvent9_1.name: Yo
talkEvent9_1.value: Nai, ¿podrías decirme específicamente el castigo del que hablaste antes?

talkEvent9_3.value: Ella baja la cabeza y mira a su alrededor para escapar del contacto visual conmigo. Ella obviamente está mostrando una actitud evasiva.

talkEvent9_4.name: Yo
talkEvent9_4.value: Nai, por favor dime. No tengo la intencion de hacerlo.

talkEvent9_7.name: Yo
talkEvent9_7.value: ..... Quizás, si me lo dices, ¿pueda ayudarte con ello?

talkEvent9_9.value: Me mira por un momento y parece decidirse a responder mi pregunta con una voz tan baja como el zumbido de un mosquito.

talkEvent9_10.name: Nai
talkEvent9_10.value: .... Esa persona ... me ... obligaba ... a hacer cosas que no queria

talkEvent9_11.value: Después de eso, ella baja la cabeza y se pierde en un extraño estado de ánimo depresivo. Mejor no digo más.

talkEvent10_2.value: Nai sigue mirándome, llena de ansiedad en sus ojos.

talkEvent10_4.name: Nai
talkEvent10_4.value: ... Entonces ... Perdón ... por dejarle gastar algo de dinero en mí ...

talkEvent10_7.name: Yo
talkEvent10_7.value: La compensación no es gran cosa. Pero ... Tengo curiosidad, ¿por qué intentaste robar un pastel?

talkEvent10_8.name: Nai
talkEvent10_8.value: ... El pastel ... se veia ... muy delicioso ..

talkEvent10_9.name: Yo
talkEvent10_9.value: Pero robar no es bueno Nai. No puedes hacerlo simplemente porque quieres comerlo y sin pedir permiso a otros. Eso es ---- robar.

talkEvent10_10.name: Nai
talkEvent10_10.value: ...Lo siento. Soy consciente de mi error ... Señor ... ¿me abandonará por esto? Nunca lo volveré a hacer. ¡No me atrevere a hacerlo de nuevo!

talkEvent10_11.value: La forma en que Nai lo explica con prisa y preocupación de repente toca mi corazón.

talkEvent10_12.name: Yo
talkEvent10_12.value: No quiero culparte, pero quizás no entiendas lo que has hecho. Solo quiero decirte que no es correcto lo que hiciste.

talkEvent10_13.name: Yo
talkEvent10_13.value: Si quieres comer pasteles, solo dímelo. Los compraré para ti. Pero robar definitivamente no está permitido. ¿Lo comprendes?

talkEvent10_14.name: Yo
talkEvent10_14.value: (Esta pobre niña, me temo, no tiene ni la menor idea de lo que está mal y lo que está bien).

talkEvent11_3.value: Tengo que asimilar lo obvio, tal vez haya alguna conexión entre robar pasteles y su cumpleaños.

talkEvent11_4.name: Yo
talkEvent11_4.value: Nai. ¿Quizás tu papá y tu mamá celebraban tu cumpleaños?

talkEvent11_6.value: Nai me mira muy asustada. Ella tiembla un poco. Es como si hubiera escuchado las noticias de los desastres de este siglo.

talkEvent11_7.name: Yo
talkEvent11_7.value: (¿Qué le ocurre a esta chica? ... ¿Acaso hay algo malo con lo que acabo de preguntar?)

talkEvent12_1.name: Yo
talkEvent12_1.value: Nai. ¿Tienes tus propios sueños o algo que te gustaría hacer?

talkEvent12_2.name: Nai
talkEvent12_2.value: Solo quiero servirle, señor ... Seré un como un perro para usted por el resto de mi vida.

talkEvent12_3.value: Que Nai se autodenomine asi siempre conmocionó mis capacidades. Aunque poco a poco me acostumbro, todavía me sorprende la manera en la que se llama

talkEvent12_4.name: Yo
talkEvent12_4.value: Nai, no necesitas ser el perro de nadie. Solo tienes que ser tú misma.

talkEvent12_5.name: Nai
talkEvent12_5.value: ...De ninguna manera. Si no trato de ser un perro obediente, Usted ... Señor ... definitivamente me odiará, e incluso ...

talkEvent12_6.value: La voz de Nai baja su intensidad.

talkEvent12_7.name: Yo
talkEvent12_7.value: No sé por qué tienes tantas ideas despiadadas hacia ti misma, pero escucha Nai, nunca haré nada de eso.

talkEvent12_9.value: Nai una vez más muestra su expresión de confusion mientras es humilde y adorable.

talkEvent12_10.name: Nai
talkEvent12_10.value: ... Por qué ... es tan .... diferente de lo que sé ...

talkEvent12_11.value: Ella murmura como si perdiera su alma.

talkEvent13_1.name: Yo
talkEvent13_1.value: Nai ¿Has ido a la escuela alguna vez? ¿Hay alguna asignatura en la que destaques?

talkEvent13_2.name: Nai
talkEvent13_2.value: ....¿Asignatura? No he estado en la escuela por mucho tiempo ... Pero realmente me gusta limpiar y también soy buena para lamer los platos.

talkEvent13_4.value: No puedo creer lo que acabo de escuchar.

talkEvent13_5.name: Nai
talkEvent13_5.value: Señor, aunque no he estado en la escuela por mucho tiempo, y no me va bien en las asignaturas, realmente estoy trabajando muy duro ...

talkEvent13_6.name: Nai
talkEvent13_6.value: Ya sea la comida restante en los platos sus zapatos sucios, puedo lamerlos hasta que queden limpios ... Señor, ¡por favor no me abandones!

talkEvent13_7.name: Yo
talkEvent13_7.value: Nai, ¡por favor calmate! Nunca dije que te abandonaría.

talkEvent13_8.value: Al escuchar eso, Nai finalmente se calma por su ansiedad y respira hondo.

talkEvent13_9.name: Nai
talkEvent13_9.value: ... Mientras no me abandones, señor yo ...

talkEvent13_10.name: Yo
talkEvent13_10.value: Nai, ya sean platos o cualquier otra cosa sucia, no necesitas lamerlas. Todo lo que necesito es que disfrutes de tu juventud y vivas una vida feliz todos los días de tu vida.

talkEvent13_11.name: Nai
talkEvent13_11.value: ....¿Señor? Yo ... realmente no puedo entender sus palabras ...

talkEvent13_12.name: Yo
talkEvent13_12.value: Entonces solo trabaja duro hasta acostumbrarte a una vida normal.

talkEvent13_13.name: Nai
talkEvent13_13.value: ... Aunque no lo entiendo bien, haré todo lo posible para hacer todo lo que desee siempre que me lo pida.

talkEvent14_1.name: Yo
talkEvent14_1.value: Nai ¿tienes alguna comida que te guste?

talkEvent14_3.name: Yo
talkEvent14_3.value: Si es así, por favor dime. Puedo hacerla para ti.

talkEvent14_4.value: La cara de Nai tiene una mirada sorprendida, como si hubiera escuchado algo muy absurdo.

talkEvent14_5.name: Nai
talkEvent14_5.value: ... No ... No es necesario ..... No tengo derecho a comer en su mesa ...

talkEvent14_7.name: Nai
talkEvent14_7.value: Porque ... siempre fue así ... Soy una basura baja y vil y no puedo comer en la mesa ...

talkEvent14_8.name: Yo
talkEvent14_8.value: (Esta niña no podía comer en la mesa, entonces, ¿cómo come sus comidas ...?)

talkEvent14_9.value: Algunas palabras desagradables como "perro" y "lamer los platos" me vinieron a la mente, no pude evitar pensar en una escena aterradora e infortunada ...

talkEvent14_10.value: Miro a Nai de una manera mucho más compleja ...

talkEvent14_11.name: Yo
talkEvent14_11.value: (No ... de ninguna manera ... ¿Realmente hay alguien en este mundo que sea tan cruel como para dejar que una chica tan linda coma despercios como un perro? "

talkEvent15_1.name: Yo
talkEvent15_1.value: Nai, ¿a dónde solías ir para divertirte?

talkEvent15_2.value: Nai no habla y sacude la cabeza.

talkEvent15_4.value: Nai me mira con ansiedad, con miedo en sus ojos.

talkEvent15_5.name: Nai
talkEvent15_5.value: A mi ... no me gustan los lugares llenos de gente.

talkEvent15_7.name: Nai
talkEvent15_7.value: ... sí ... especialmente ... hombres ... pero no tengo miedo a usted señor, usted es un buen hombre ...

talkEvent15_9.value: Parece como si una esposa estuviera tratando de molestando a su esposo. La expresión torpe de Nai agrega un poco de relajación a este tema algo serio.

talkEvent15_10.name: Yo
talkEvent15_10.value: Gracias por hablar bien de mí. No te decepcionaré, Nai.

talkEvent15_12.value: Aunque la mirada inocente de Nai me agrada, tengo que pensar ---

talkEvent15_13.name: Yo
talkEvent15_13.value: (¿Qué demonios le han para que se vuelva lejana de hombres?)

talkEvent16_1.name: Yo
talkEvent16_1.value: Nai, ¿que te ha parecido despues de la primera visita?

talkEvent16_2.name: Nai
talkEvent16_2.value: .... Es un poco mejor de lo que imagine ...

talkEvent16_3.name: Yo
talkEvent16_3.value: ¿En serio?. Bueno, mientras quieras hacerlo, puedes hacerlo.

talkEvent16_5.name: Yo
talkEvent16_5.value: Espero que con mi ayuda, puedas abrir tu corazón lentamente y poco a poco llevarte bien con la comunidad y los grupos.

talkEvent16_6.name: Nai
talkEvent16_6.value: Por esto ... No estoy segura de poder hacerlo ... Hoy, cuando salimos, todavía me sentía un poco asustada al principio.

talkEvent16_7.name: Yo
talkEvent16_7.value: Pero como dijiste, te sentiste un poco mejor de lo que imaginaste.

talkEvent16_8.name: Nai
talkEvent16_8.value: ... Eso es porque está conmigo. Por eso no escapé señor.

talkEvent16_9.name: Yo
talkEvent16_9.value: Si es así, ¿fui yo quien te dio la fuerza y el coraje?

talkEvent16_10.name: Nai
talkEvent16_10.value: .... Sí ... Usted a mi alrededor, no tendré tanto miedo ...

talkEvent16_11.name: Yo
talkEvent16_11.value: Me honras al decir eso, Nai.

talkEvent17_3.value: Nai parece pensar en algo. Después de un rato, ella asiente con la cabeza ligeramente.

talkEvent17_4.name: Nai
talkEvent17_4.value: ... anteriormente ... fui con mi papá y mi mamá ...

talkEvent17_7.value: Nai parece no estar dispuesta a responder mi pregunta. Cambiare el tema por ahora.

talkEvent17_8.name: Yo
talkEvent17_8.value: ¿Debío ser muy divertido salir? ¿Tenías miedo de los extraños en ese entonces?

talkEvent17_9.name: Nai
talkEvent17_9.value: ... Mamá estaba conmigo, así que no tenía miedo ... Es un hermoso recuerdo ...

talkEvent17_10.name: Yo
talkEvent17_10.value: Ese es realmente un buen recuerdo. Debe ser porque estabas rodeada de cosas tan buenas que podrías convertirte en una chica tan buena como ahora.

talkEvent17_12.name: Yo
talkEvent17_12.value: (¿Dije algo malo? ¿Por qué puso una expresión triste de repente?)

talkEvent18_1.name: Yo
talkEvent18_1.value: Nai, ¿a dónde te gusta ir más?

talkEvent18_3.name: Yo
talkEvent18_3.value: oh ... montañas nevadas ... que curioso. ¿Por qué te gustan las montañas nevadas?

talkEvent18_5.value: Ella guarda silencio y no estoy seguro de lo que está pensando. Sus cejas fruncen el ceño con fuerza como si le hubiera arrojado una pregunta incontestable.

talkEvent18_7.name: Nai
talkEvent18_7.value: ... a Nai le gusta el invierno .....

talkEvent18_8.name: Yo
talkEvent18_8.value: ¿Invierno? Mm ... supongo que te gusta la nieve?

talkEvent18_9.name: Nai
talkEvent18_9.value: ... s ... Sí, me gusta la nieve.

talkEvent18_10.value: Esta es la primera vez que veo una sonrisa que se puede llamar sonrisa.

talkEvent18_11.value: Parece estar perdida en algún tipo de hermoso recuerdo ...

talkEvent18_12.name: Yo
talkEvent18_12.value: (Parece que el invierno, la nieve y las montañas le han traído recuerdos agradables. ¿Debe ser un hermoso recuerdo con su familia?)

talkEvent19_4.value: Nai de repente abre mucho los ojos, con puro placer e inocencia cruel. Ella comienza a quitarse la ropa con algo de miedo.

talkEvent19_7.name: Yo
talkEvent19_7.value: ...¿En que clase de juegos necesitas quitarte la ropa? ...

talkEvent19_8.name: Nai
talkEvent19_8.value: ¿Señor, no lo sabes? Esa persona a menudo jugaba conmigo ... Déjeme quitarme toda la ropa y arrodillarme en las escaleras ... y luego ...

talkEvent19_9.name: Yo
talkEvent19_9.value: Espera ... ¡Nai! Quitarse la ropa ... ¡este no es un juego divertido!

talkEvent19_10.value: Los ojos redondos de Nai muestran desilusión y perplejidad.

talkEvent19_11.name: Nai
talkEvent19_11.value: ... Señor ... ¿no te gusta este juego? Lo siento, no lo haré. Pero ... a esa persona le gustaba mucho ...

talkEvent19_12.name: Yo
talkEvent19_12.value: No me gusta ... por favor, no lo vuelvas a hacer más.

talkEvent19_13.name: Yo
talkEvent19_13.value: (No soy ese tipo de bicho raro)

talkEvent20_1.name: Yo
talkEvent20_1.value: Nai ... cof ... cof ... ¿Por qué jugar a este juego? Me refiero a quitarse la ropa ...

talkEvent20_3.value: Nai muestra una expresión muy firme, no podía saber cómo responderle.

talkEvent20_4.name: Yo
talkEvent20_4.value: (Si esto es normal ... ¿qué tal lo anormal? Jesús, no podría pensar más).

talkEvent20_6.name: Yo
talkEvent20_6.value: ...¡Por supuesto no! ¿Quién jugará un juego tan anormal?

talkEvent20_7.name: Nai
talkEvent20_7.value: ...¿Anormal? No lo entiendo ... Cuando hacia algo mal ... O si esa persona se sentia infeliz, me pedirá que juegue con él para hacerlo feliz.

talkEvent20_8.name: Yo
talkEvent20_8.value: ...¡Qué demonios es eso! ¡Nunca escuché sobre esto!

talkEvent20_9.name: Nai
talkEvent20_9.value: ... Eso ... ¿Cuál es el problema con eso?

talkEvent21_1.name: Yo
talkEvent21_1.value: Nai, quiero hablarte en serio sobre este llamado "juego".

talkEvent21_3.name: Yo
talkEvent21_3.value: Nai, antes que nada, eres una persona libre.

talkEvent21_5.name: Yo
talkEvent21_5.value: No, escúchame, eres un humano y un humano debe tener una personalidad independiente.

talkEvent21_6.value: Me resulta difícil explicarle todo esto a Nai, como si le estuviera enseñando a un niño cuya cabeza y corazón aún no conozcan la maldad.

talkEvent21_7.name: Yo
talkEvent21_7.value: Niñas ... um ... por supuesto, inudos los niños ... Debería decir que para todos, es muy importante decidir sobre su propio cuerpo.

talkEvent21_9.name: Yo
talkEvent21_9.value: Sí, tu cuerpo, debes decidir las acciones por tu cuenta. Depende de ti si ... cof ... te quitas la ropa y eres vista, en lugar de obedecer las órdenes de alguien.

talkEvent21_10.name: Nai
talkEvent21_10.value: ... yo ... no entiendo ... ¿Mi cuerpo indecente no puede ser visto por otros? ...

talkEvent21_11.name: Yo
talkEvent21_11.value: No me refiero a eso. Solo debes decidirlo tu misma. Tal vez podrías mostrárselo a las personas que quieres.

talkEvent21_12.name: Nai
talkEvent21_12.value: ¿Puedo decidir por mí misma a la persona que quiero?

talkEvent21_13.value: Nai parece no entender lo que dije, pero tal vez ella entiende algo. Ella piensa sobre mis palabras y se pierde en un pensamiento profundo.

sleepTalkEvent_1.name: Yo
sleepTalkEvent_1.value: Nai, ¿estás lista para aceptar que te toquen de los demás?

sleepTalkEvent_2.value: Recordé el primer contacto corporal con Nai y no pude evitar sonreír.

sleepTalkEvent_4.name: Nai
sleepTalkEvent_4.value: Todavía no estoy lista ... En realidad no ... a menos que sea por usted señor .....

sleepTalkEvent_5.name: Yo
sleepTalkEvent_5.value: ¿Oh? no puedes aceptar que otros te toquen pero yo soy una excepción ...

sleepTalkEvent_6.value: La respuesta de Nai indudablemente me agrada. Se puede decir que, hasta cierto punto, mi sentido de vanidad arraigado profundamente en mi corazón como hombre está muy satisfecho.

sleepTalkEvent_8.value: Después de eso, Nai mueve su cabeza de manera encantadora. No pude evitar que mi imaginación volara.

sleepTalkEvent_9.name: Yo
sleepTalkEvent_9.value: ... Cof ... cof ... Entonces podemos trabajar duro lentamente para que aceptes dejarte tocar por otros.

sleepTalkEvent_10.name: Yo
sleepTalkEvent_10.value: (aunque realmente espero que solo aceptes que yo te toque).

talkEvent23_1.name: Yo
talkEvent23_1.value: Nai, ¿qué te pasa hoy? me miras todo el tiempo

talkEvent23_2.name: Yo
talkEvent23_2.value: (desde ayer, ella ha actuado más diferente que antes ...)

talkEvent23_4.value: Nai quiere decir algo pero no dice nada. Ella parece atrapada en esta situación.

talkEvent23_6.name: Nai
talkEvent23_6.value: ... Señor, en estos días ... me he sentido ... muy ansiosa ...

talkEvent23_7.name: Yo
talkEvent23_7.value: ¿Por qué? ¿Hay algo que haya hecho para hacerte sentir miedo?

talkEvent23_8.name: Nai
talkEvent23_8.value: ¡No, para nada Señor, eres tan bueno! Soy yo. Siento que soy inútil, y no puedo ayudarlo, señor.

talkEvent23_9.name: Nai
talkEvent23_9.value: Si es posible, ¿puede permitirme trabajar para ganar dinero para la familia? De esta manera no sentiré que soy inútil para usted, señor.

talkEvent23_10.name: Yo
talkEvent23_10.value: (Si digo que no, podria ser mucho más difícil sacarla de la ansiedad ...)

talkEvent23_12.name: Nai
talkEvent23_12.value: Gracias señor por darme la oportunidad de dedicarle mi cuerpo y trabajo a usted.

talkEvent24_1.name: Yo
talkEvent24_1.value: Si vas a trabajar, ¿tienes algo que te interese?

talkEvent24_2.name: Nai
talkEvent24_2.value: ...aún no. No lo he pensado detenidamente.

talkEvent24_3.name: Yo
talkEvent24_3.value: Esto es realmente un dolor de cabeza. Déjame pensar en ello.

talkEvent24_4.name: Nai
talkEvent24_4.value: Pero deseo estar en el trabajo que tenga algo que ver con el señor. Quiero acercarme a su mundo.

talkEvent24_5.name: Yo
talkEvent24_5.value: ¿Yo? Entonces no hay problema. Déjame ayudarte a encontrar tu trabajo.

talkEvent24_7.name: Yo
talkEvent24_7.value: (¿Qué debe hacer Nai? Esto debo considerarlo bien ...)

talkEvent25_1.name: Yo
talkEvent25_1.value: Justo ahora el administrador me llamó por teléfono. Habló sobre lo bien que te ha ido en el trabajo.

talkEvent25_3.name: Yo
talkEvent25_3.value: Sí, has sido reconocido por otros.

talkEvent25_5.name: Yo
talkEvent25_5.value: Por supuesto, me siento orgulloso de ti Nai.

talkEvent25_6.name: Nai
talkEvent25_6.value: Entonces trabajaré más duro para hacer un mejor trabajo en la biblioteca

talkEvent25_7.name: Yo
talkEvent25_7.value: El trabajo es importante, pero también debes cuidar tu cuerpo.

talkEvent26_1.name: Yo
talkEvent26_1.value: Nai.¿Piensas por qué la gente tiene que trabajar?

talkEvent26_2.name: Nai
talkEvent26_2.value: Porque si no trabajo, me convertiré en un desperdicio inútil ...

talkEvent26_4.value: Ella siente mi desaprobación y se muerde los labios. Ella piensa con mucho cuidado por un momento y finalmente dice

talkEvent26_5.name: Nai
talkEvent26_5.value: ¿Porque si no trabajan, las personas no podrán darse cuenta de sus capacidades ...? y.... ¿No tendré mi propio valor ...?

talkEvent26_6.name: Yo
talkEvent26_6.value: Sí ... esa respuesta está casi por ahí. Sin trabajo su valor no se realizarán.

talkEvent26_7.name: Yo
talkEvent26_7.value: Permitir que trabajes no te ayuda a ser útil, si no que te ayuda a establecer tu propio carácter.

talkEvent26_9.name: Nai
talkEvent26_9.value: ... sí, me parece un poco más comprensible

talkEvent26_10.name: Nai
talkEvent26_10.value: Mientras estoy en el trabajo, a veces no me siento mal ...

talkEvent26_11.name: Yo
talkEvent26_11.value: Eso es. Una vez que te distingues, puedes encontrar lentamente tu fuerza y ​​luego ser positivo contigo mismo.

talkEvent27_1.name: Yo
talkEvent27_1.value: Nai, has comenzado a trabajar y tendrás ingresos en el futuro. ¿Has pensado en cómo gastarlo?

talkEvent27_4.name: Nai
talkEvent27_4.value: ... Por supuesto que se lo daré, señor. ¿Cómo puedo tomar decisiones sobre cómo gastar el dinero?

talkEvent27_5.value: No me parece extraño que Nai tenga tales ideas.

talkEvent27_6.name: Yo
talkEvent27_6.value: Nai, escucha esto, el ingreso se obtiene por tu trabajo y te pertenece, por lo que, por supuesto, tienes el derecho de gastarlo como quieras.

talkEvent27_9.value: Intento parecer serio. Espero que se dé cuenta de lo serio e importante que es este tema.

talkEvent27_10.name: Nai
talkEvent27_10.value: ... No hay nada que me pertenezca. Señor, estoy sorprendida de que me dé tal previlige ...

talkEvent27_11.name: Yo
talkEvent27_11.value: ... Ah, Nai, no me importa por lo que has pasado. Pero a partir de ahora, puedes tener todo tipo de facultades razonables, ¿entiendes?

talkEvent27_12.name: Nai
talkEvent27_12.value: ... Aunque no pueda entenderlo ni pueda acostumbrarme a ello por ahora, haré todo lo posible para adaptarme a lo que el señor me ha dicho ...

talkEvent28_3.name: Nai
talkEvent28_3.value: Mucho antes, solo había un niño en mi familia ...

talkEvent28_4.name: Yo
talkEvent28_4.value: ¿Eres hija única? Entonces debiste tener todo el amor de la familia.

talkEvent28_6.value: Nai de repente se deprime, como si hubiera dicho algo malo.

talkEvent30_3.value: Nai responde al instante. Parece que ella ha pensado en esa pregunta muchas veces.

talkEvent30_4.name: Yo
talkEvent30_4.value: Por supuesto. Si tienes hermanos y hermanas, la vida será más divertida.

talkEvent30_5.name: Yo
talkEvent30_5.value: Incluso si tienes una mejor amiga, es posible que ella no pueda quedarse contigo en todo momento. En casa, estarás solo y te sentirás solo, ¿verdad?

talkEvent30_6.name: Nai
talkEvent30_6.value: ... Um ... yo ... solo siento que ... mis hermanos o hermanas ... tal vez ...ellos me protegerian ...

talkEvent30_8.value: Pienso en las palabras de Nai y me siento muy extraño por un momento. Pero no puedo entenderlo.

talkEvent30_9.name: Yo
talkEvent30_9.value: (¿Por qué Nai cree que necesita la protección de sus hermanos y hermanas ...? ¿Alguien intentaria lastimarla?)

talkEvent31_1.name: Yo
talkEvent31_1.value: Do you have any other friends?

talkEvent31_3.name: Nai
talkEvent31_3.value: "She" knows about all of my secrets...

talkEvent31_4.name: Yo
talkEvent31_4.value: All secrets? Wow, then she must be your best friend. If possible, I would like to meet her.

talkEvent31_6.value: With that, Nai' eyes gloom and it looks like she's fallen into the deep grief

talkEvent31_7.value: What do you mean by that, Nai? Any accidents happening to her friend?

talkEvent32_1.name: Yo
talkEvent32_1.value: Do you have any memory about school?

talkEvent32_2.name: Nai
talkEvent32_2.value: ...I haven't been to schoool for a long time, just could not remember it.

talkEvent32_3.name: Yo
talkEvent32_3.value: Do you have any beautiful memories in your school days?

talkEvent32_5.name: Yo
talkEvent32_5.value: (seems to poking at her pain spots)

talkEvent32_6.name: Yo
talkEvent32_6.value: Then we can work together. I can teach you how to become adorable. Then you must have a lot of friends.

talkEvent32_7.value: Nai looks at me with gratitude--

teachGetTalkEvent_1.name: Yo
teachGetTalkEvent_1.value: Besides working part-time, do you think about going back to school?

teachGetTalkEvent_3.value: Nai's eyes blink with puzzlement and she seems not able to understand the simple sentence that I just said.

teachGetTalkEvent_4.name: Nai
teachGetTalkEvent_4.value: ..I havn't been to school for a very very long time...There're so many people in school.

teachGetTalkEvent_5.name: Yo
teachGetTalkEvent_5.value: If you go to school, you can learn a great deal of new knowledge so you could help me better.

teachGetTalkEvent_6.value: At this moment, I am the Satan transformed into a snake and throwing an olive branch of temptation

teachGetTalkEvent_7.name: Nai
teachGetTalkEvent_7.value: ...Since it is something that will be helpful for you sir, I will be sure to do it.

teachGetTalkEvent_8.name: Yo
teachGetTalkEvent_8.value: Good girl. In school you can get to know more friends, learn more things and will definitely be more happy.

teachGetTalkEvent_9.name: Nai
teachGetTalkEvent_9.value: As long as you are with me, I will be very happy.

talkEvent34_1.name: Yo
talkEvent34_1.value: What does it feel like to go to school?

talkEvent34_2.name: Nai
talkEvent34_2.value: ...er...nervous...scared...There're so many people that I do not know in school...

talkEvent34_3.name: Yo
talkEvent34_3.value: you will get used to it slowly... Get in touch more with teachers and students....

talkEvent34_4.name: Nai
talkEvent34_4.value: ...Sure, I will work hard on that.

talkEvent34_5.name: Yo
talkEvent34_5.value: But..if anyone tries to bully you, you have to tell me in the first place. I will seek justice for you

talkEvent34_6.name: Nai
talkEvent34_6.value: ....Thank you very much sir....Actually I.... am not worthwhile for you sir to do so.

talkEvent34_7.value: Hearing what Nai said, I tap on her forehead gently.

talkEvent34_8.name: Yo
talkEvent34_8.value: I have said it many times. You have your own values. I don't like the way you talk about yourself.

talkEvent34_9.name: Nai
talkEvent34_9.value: ..Sorry, sir. I will work hard to mend it...

talkEvent35_1.name: Yo
talkEvent35_1.value: Which do you prefer, work or study?

talkEvent35_2.name: Nai
talkEvent35_2.value: ....I do not like neither of them....

talkEvent35_4.name: Nai
talkEvent35_4.value: ..No...because the two things will make me get in touch with many strangers...

talkEvent35_5.name: Yo
talkEvent35_5.value: (It is a bit rush to let Nai get used to meeting strangers so quickly.)

talkEvent35_6.name: Nai
talkEvent35_6.value: ...But I will try for it, because I have promised it for you Sir

talkEvent35_7.value: She makes her promise in a really sincere way, which touches my heart deeply.

talkEvent35_8.name: Yo
talkEvent35_8.value: Yes, you are definitely able to do it.

talkEvent36_1.name: Yo
talkEvent36_1.value: Why did you not go to school? Could you tell me?

talkEvent36_4.name: Nai
talkEvent36_4.value: It was meaningless for me to go to school....

talkEvent36_5.name: Nai
talkEvent36_5.value: "No matter how well I do in school, I am still troublesome rubbish".....If I go to school, it not only is a waste of time and money but also a disgrace to the school.

talkEvent36_6.name: Yo
talkEvent36_6.value: ...Please forget about those odd theories. I don't think so at all.

talkEvent36_7.name: Nai
talkEvent36_7.value: I know sir, you are a little different.

talkEvent36_8.name: Yo
talkEvent36_8.value: You will become better some day. But before that you must forget all the bullshit of that person.

talkEvent37_1.name: Yo
talkEvent37_1.value: Is there anything fun today at school?

talkEvent37_2.name: Nai
talkEvent37_2.value: ....I did not pay attention to that...

talkEvent37_3.name: Yo
talkEvent37_3.value: Don't just study all the time. You also need to take a look at things surrounding you.

talkEvent37_4.name: Nai
talkEvent37_4.value: .....I am not interested in any people but Sir.

talkEvent37_5.name: Yo
talkEvent37_5.value: Although I feel happy with what you said, I still hope that you can make more friends.

talkEvent37_6.name: Nai
talkEvent37_6.value: ....Got it. I will take your advice, Sir.

talkTeacherCurse1_1.name: Yo
talkTeacherCurse1_1.value: Nai, what's going on with you?

talkTeacherCurse1_3.name: Yo
talkTeacherCurse1_3.value: You wept? Your eyes are red...

talkTeacherCurse1_4.name: Nai
talkTeacherCurse1_4.value: I got blamed by the teacher.

talkTeacherCurse1_5.name: Yo
talkTeacherCurse1_5.value: Why did the teacher blame you? Could you tell me?

talkTeacherCurse1_6.name: Yo
talkTeacherCurse1_6.value: (This girl is clearly so obedient and cute)

talkTeacherCurse1_7.name: Nai
talkTeacherCurse1_7.value: Maybe because I.....cannot get along well with classmates....

talkTeacherCurse1_8.name: Yo
talkTeacherCurse1_8.value: That's how it is. Rome was not built in a day. Nai, you need to learn how to get along with classmates gradually. I am confident that you can do it.

talkTeacherCurse1_11.name: Yo
talkTeacherCurse1_11.value: Good girl, don't weep any more.

talkEvent38_1.name: Yo
talkEvent38_1.value: So, how about your homework today? All finished?

talkEvent38_3.name: Yo
talkEvent38_3.value: Looks like someone is being lazy...Don't study with emotions...Even if the teacher blames you, you still need to finish your assignments.

talkEvent38_5.value: Nai looks at me pathetically. I felt a slight sense of coquetry.

talkEvent38_6.name: Nai
talkEvent38_6.value: The writing lesson is really difficult..I do not know how to write articles.

talkEvent38_7.value: I could not hiding my pleaseure...I could only pinch her face in a spoiled way

talkEvent38_8.name: Yo
talkEvent38_8.value: This is so easy...do you forget that I am a journalist?

talkEvent38_10.name: Yo
talkEvent38_10.value: If you do not know about writing, let me teach you.

talkEvent38_12.name: Yo
talkEvent38_12.value: If you have any problems in writing assignments, just come to ask me

talkEvent39_4.name: Yo
talkEvent39_4.value: Why do you ask about it suddenly?

talkEvent39_5.name: Nai
talkEvent39_5.value: In class, the teacher asked me about my dream...But I...was not well aware of what dream is....

talkEvent39_6.name: Yo
talkEvent39_6.value: A dream is something that you are bent on doing even though you know clearly that you are going to fail.

talkEvent39_8.value: Nai seems not to be able to understand the firm attitude people hold towards dreams

talkEvent39_9.name: Yo
talkEvent39_9.value: Maybe it really is a strange thing. For example, I always looked forward to becoming a maths professor but even if I joined the interest society I still could not make it..Hahaha

talkEvent39_10.name: Yo
talkEvent39_10.value: But, people who have dreams will glitter like gold

talkEvent39_12.name: Nai
talkEvent39_12.value: Sir you are the gold that glitters in my eyes....

talkWork2Get1_4.name: Nai
talkWork2Get1_4.value: Sir....I want to have an extra job...

talkWork2Get1_6.name: Nai
talkWork2Get1_6.value: Sir you mentioned that I should save some money. I want to save a little more money...

talkWork2Get1_7.name: Yo
talkWork2Get1_7.value: Oh I see. It is good for you to have such an idea.

talkWork2Get1_9.name: Yo
talkWork2Get1_9.value: Of course, this is on me. But you need to consider your health. If you feel too tired to carry on, you must tell me.

talkWork2Get1_11.name: Yo
talkWork2Get1_11.value: OK, just leave everything else to me then.

talkWork2End_1.name: Yo
talkWork2End_1.value: How is it going for your new job?

talkWork2End_2.name: Nai
talkWork2End_2.value: ....Just so so...It's just meeting so many people everyday..

talkWork2End_5.name: Yo
talkWork2End_5.value: This is progress. Keep meeting more people and I will gradually recognize yourself.

talkEvent40_1.name: Yo
talkEvent40_1.value: When working at the hotel, was the boss good to you?

talkEvent40_3.value: Nai is hesitating and her words get stuck in her throat.

talkEvent40_5.name: Nai
talkEvent40_5.value: ...The guests that came to the hotel were a bit strange..

talkEvent40_7.name: Nai
talkEvent40_7.value: They would speak something that I could not understand and laugh in a way that made me very uncomfortable

talkEvent40_8.name: Yo
talkEvent40_8.value: (Probably she met with some ganster that loved to talk dirty)

talkEvent40_9.name: Yo
talkEvent40_9.value: Just turn a deaf ear to those people. Take care and be safe. If anybody dares to touch you, just seek help from your boss, you know that?

talkEvent41_1.name: Yo
talkEvent41_1.value: Nai, what do you think is the most important trait of a person?

talkEvent41_3.name: Yo
talkEvent41_3.value: ...This is not training animals. Obeying orders is the requirement of an animal trainer to animals.

talkEvent41_5.value: Nai is really confused and asks me with innocent eyes.

talkEvent41_6.name: Yo
talkEvent41_6.value: Of course, they are totally different. We are humans and we are high-level animals, different from the beasts.

talkEvent41_8.name: Yo
talkEvent41_8.value: So you must remember at any time that you are a human and what's most important for a human is to have independent personality.

talkEvent41_9.name: Yo
talkEvent41_9.value: As for obeying the orders, you need to gradually forget that from the depth of your brain.

talkEvent41_10.name: Nai
talkEvent41_10.value: ....Yes, I will obey every order from you Sir.

talkEvent41_11.name: Yo
talkEvent41_11.value: (What I have just said does not make any difference at all.)

talkEvent42_1.name: Yo
talkEvent42_1.value: Nai, let's talk about what is independent personality. Do you have any idea?

talkEvent42_3.value: After Nai asks, she seems to feel that she should not ask that way and apologize to me in a hurry--

talkEvent42_4.name: Nai
talkEvent42_4.value: Sir...sorry, I am so stupid...I do not know anything...Sir please forgive my ignorance....

talkEvent42_5.name: Yo
talkEvent42_5.value: Nai, I have never thought you are stupid, so you don't need to belittle yourself so much.

talkEvent42_6.name: Yo
talkEvent42_6.value: Independent personality refers to the independence, initiative and creativity that everyone has. Do you remember it well?

talkEvent42_7.name: Yo
talkEvent42_7.value: Once we have independent personality, we will not over-rely on any external spiritual authority.

talkEvent42_8.value: Nor will we rely on some forces in reality. In the pursuit of truth, we will develop the ability to think and make judgement on one's own.

talkEvent42_9.name: Yo
talkEvent42_9.value: Independent personality is not something that can be achieved in a short time.

talkEvent42_10.value: Maybe it takes over ten year or even decades to explore and think about it..

talkEvent42_11.value: With that, I feel it is too complicated to understand. I look down at Nai. Not suprisingly, Nai looks puzzled and confused.

talkEvent42_12.name: Yo
talkEvent42_12.value: Welll, just drop it. This is not something that can be learned fast. Let's do it in a step-by-step manner.

talkEvent43_3.name: Nai
talkEvent43_3.value: ....The independent personality that you talked about....I still could not understand...

talkEvent43_5.value: One great idea suddenly comes to my mind.

talkEvent43_6.name: Yo
talkEvent43_6.value: This sounds very complicated, right? But simply put, we can try to understand from one thing.

talkEvent43_7.name: Yo
talkEvent43_7.value: For example, what that god said was not necessarily right and needed to be followed...

talkEvent43_8.name: Yo
talkEvent43_8.value: If you feel unreasonable, unhappy or unwilling, you can speak it loud that you don't want it. You can reject and violate the orders of the so-called God.

talkEvent43_10.value: It is as if Nai hears something ground-breaking. She opens her eyes wide and looks at me, with doubt over her face.

talkEvent43_11.name: Nai
talkEvent43_11.value: But violating orders will bring horrible punishment...

talkEvent43_12.name: Yo
talkEvent43_12.value: Yes, for independent people, she has the right to refuse anything that she does not want to do, and for that she does not need to bear any punishment.

talkEvent43_13.name: Yo
talkEvent43_13.value: Maybe we can try for now? Right now I have you by my side and I will protect you from getting hurt.

talkEvent43_14.name: Nai
talkEvent43_14.value: ...um....If you are with me, maybe I can have a try.

talkEvent44_2.value: Nai frowns her eyebrows and thinks about it. How cute and sweet she looks in that way.

talkEvent44_5.name: Yo
talkEvent44_5.value: Then you can take your time to think about it

talkEvent44_6.name: Nai
talkEvent44_6.value: ....My hair color. Does that count? I ...am rather fond of this color...

talkEvent44_7.name: Yo
talkEvent44_7.value: Of course. Because this color was as good-looking as Mom?

talkEvent44_9.value: Only when talking about Mom will Nai's face show the rare and warm smile.

talkEvent44_10.name: Yo
talkEvent44_10.value: Since this is your favorite color, it will also be mine.

talkEvent44_11.value: I know clearly that I have always wished to see that smile on her face.

talkEvent45_1.name: Yo
talkEvent45_1.value: You love Mom very much. Can you talk more about her?

talkEvent45_3.name: Nai
talkEvent45_3.value: Sir, you are a very gentle and soft person just like Mom.

talkEvent45_4.name: Yo
talkEvent45_4.value: She must love you very much. You must have very intersting experiences.

talkEvent45_5.name: Nai
talkEvent45_5.value: ..Yes. Long long ago, Mom took me to see the snow...Snow is very beautiful....beautiful..

talkEvent45_6.name: Yo
talkEvent45_6.value: So you loved winter because of that?

talkEvent45_8.name: Yo
talkEvent45_8.value: That must be a very wonderful memory.

talkEvent45_9.name: Nai
talkEvent45_9.value: ...I will never forget that all my life.

talkEvent46_1.name: Yo
talkEvent46_1.value: Nai, could you tell me more about your past?

talkEvent46_3.name: Yo
talkEvent46_3.value: I just want to know more about you.

talkEvent46_5.value: Nai seems not willing to talk about her past. I will not force her to do that, either.

talkEvent46_6.name: Yo
talkEvent46_6.value: If you still don't want to talk, please don't force it. I will wait for the day to come when you are willing to tell me.

talkEvent47_1.value: I really want to learn more about Nai's past. But she seems not to trust me so much.

talkEvent47_2.value: As I feel frustrated thinking about this, she suddenly whispers to me--

talkEvent47_3.name: Nai
talkEvent47_3.value: ...Sir, do you want to know things about me?

talkEvent47_4.value: Are you willing to tell me?

talkEvent47_5.name: Yo
talkEvent47_5.value: This question represents trust so it makes me super excited.

talkEvent47_7.name: Yo
talkEvent47_7.value: ...Perhaps, you can tell me something about that person...The God in your world. Who is he?

talkEvent47_9.value: It looks like I have started a bad topic and Nai emotions go down all at once and it seems black clouds are gathering nearby.

talkEvent47_10.name: Yo
talkEvent47_10.value: ...If really diffcult to answer, Nai can choose not to talk about it. I respect your choice...

talkEvent47_11.name: Nai
talkEvent47_11.value: My words are interrupted by your rely.

talkEvent48_1.name: Yo
talkEvent48_1.value: ...Nai, could you tell me more about your father?

talkEvent48_2.name: Nai
talkEvent48_2.value: ...Sir..you once said....If I do not want to do anyting, I can refuse, right?

talkEvent48_3.value: Nai is lost in some very depressed mood. This question seems not suitable to be asked further.

talkEvent48_4.name: Yo
talkEvent48_4.value: Yes. You don't want to answer me, right?

talkEvent48_6.name: Yo
talkEvent48_6.value: Of course. Let's stop here today.

talkEvent48_7.name: Yo
talkEvent48_7.value: (Although I don't know more, Nai at least tells me about the identity of that person...)

talkEvent48_8.name: Yo
talkEvent48_8.value: (Looks like she has trusted me more than when we first met....)

talkEvent48_9.value: Although I cannot figure out all the myths on this girl, this level of information awareness still makes me satisfied.

talkEvent49_1.name: Yo
talkEvent49_1.value: So do you have any wishes?

talkEvent49_3.value: Looking at Nai's reactions, I know the answer is positive.

talkEvent49_4.name: Yo
talkEvent49_4.value: Can you tell me about it? Just pretend that I am your best friend and share me your secrets.

talkEvent49_5.name: Nai
talkEvent49_5.value: ...Of course...But Sir, please do not make fun of me...

talkEvent49_7.value: To show my sincerity, I lift three fingers to make an oath---

talkEvent49_9.value: Nai's face shows an expression of expecting happiness...

talkEvent49_10.value: Her wishes remind me that she fought with the child next door.

talkEvent49_11.name: Yo
talkEvent49_11.value: (This girl really cares a great deal about family)

talkEvent49_12.name: Yo
talkEvent49_12.value: Very good. It is a very good and meaningful wish!

talkEvent49_13.name: Nai
talkEvent49_13.value: ...Sir....don't you think that my wish is very naive and stupid?

talkEvent49_14.name: Yo
talkEvent49_14.value: Of course not. This is a warm wish.

talkEvent50_1.name: Yo
talkEvent50_1.value: I have not expected your wish as that. If possible, I really hope to help you realize your wish.

talkEvent50_4.value: Nai looks at me smiling, as gentle as the breeze that blows under the cherry in April.

talkEvent50_7.value: Nai does not speak but look at me smiling.

talkEvent50_8.name: Yo
talkEvent50_8.value: (what does Nai mean? Does she mean that I have realized her wish?! This girl finally considers me to be her family member at the bottom of her heart?!)

talkEvent51_3.name: Yo
talkEvent51_3.value: What's wrong? Do I get dirt on my face?

talkEvent51_6.value: Nai seems not used to talking to people actively.

talkEvent51_11.value: I have never thought Nai would actively care about me. This makes me surprised and joyful.

talkEvent51_12.name: Yo
talkEvent51_12.value: For now, I only have one wish.

talkEvent51_14.value: It is rare to see Nai being eager to know about something.

talkEvent51_15.name: Yo
talkEvent51_15.value: My wish for now is that you could be happy everyday.

talkEvent52_2.value: Nai looks at me all the time

talkEvent52_3.name: Nai
talkEvent52_3.value: ....Sir, can I ask you a quesition?

talkEvent52_5.name: Nai
talkEvent52_5.value: Why do you so actively encourage me to get in touch with people?

talkEvent52_6.name: Nai
talkEvent52_6.value: Sir you must know that I am afraid to get in touch with others....

talkEvent52_7.name: Yo
talkEvent52_7.value: Um...If there's any reason, it is because I wish you to walk away from the shadown that I knew nothing about.

talkEvent52_8.name: Yo
talkEvent52_8.value: and become a happy and healthy little cutie just like other girls.

talkEvent52_10.name: Yo
talkEvent52_10.value: The more you are afraid, the more I will force you to go ahead and confront it. If you always escape from it, it will be impossible to overcome all this, won't it?

talkEvent52_11.name: Nai
talkEvent52_11.value: ....The more afraid I am...the more I have to confront it....

talkEvent52_12.value: Nai closes her eyes and speaks to herself, as if resonating with this sentence.

talkEvent53_1.name: Yo
talkEvent53_1.value: Have you joined any interest societies in school?

talkEvent53_3.name: Yo
talkEvent53_3.value: Then are you interested in any societies?

talkEvent53_4.value: I try hard to lead Nai in the hope that she can open her mind and expand her social circle and gradually become a person with normal social skills.

talkEvent53_5.name: Nai
talkEvent53_5.value: ...I will pay more attention to it....

talkEvent53_6.name: Yo
talkEvent53_6.value: Great. Hope you can find what you love to do..

talkEvent53_7.name: Nai
talkEvent53_7.value: ....Sir, do you like me in that way?

talkEvent53_8.name: Yo
talkEvent53_8.value: Of course, I wish you to have independent personality, have your own goal of pursuit. This is the manifestation of independent personality.

talkEvent53_9.value: Nai lowers her head as if thinking about the meaning of my words.

talkEvent53_10.name: Nai
talkEvent53_10.value: ...I seem to understand a bit more...I will try hard to find what I love to do, for you Sir.

talkEvent53_11.name: Yo
talkEvent53_11.value: I look forward to that day.

talkEvent54_3.name: Nai
talkEvent54_3.value: ....Sir....when you were in school, did you join any interest society?

talkEvent54_7.name: Nai
talkEvent54_7.value: ...I could not guess it out....literature society? After all, you write articles very well.

talkEvent54_8.name: Yo
talkEvent54_8.value: It might surprise you if I tell you the truth. I joined the maths society...

talkEvent54_9.name: Nai
talkEvent54_9.value: Really?..Why....It was quite far from your career.

talkEvent54_10.name: Yo
talkEvent54_10.value: Work is just about work. Interest is about interest. People tend to be somewhat rebellious. You cannot rely on interest for a living but still you need to have a go at it.

talkEvent54_12.name: Yo
talkEvent54_12.value: You can develop your interests. When you find it as you grow up, you will understand what I say.

talkEvent55_1.name: Yo
talkEvent55_1.value: Nai, you have lived with me for some time, how does it feel?

talkEvent55_2.name: Nai
talkEvent55_2.value: ....I...am just a bit unaccustomed....Sir, you have taught me a lot of stuff that I could not understand...

talkEvent55_3.name: Yo
talkEvent55_3.value: Yeah, so, will you hate me then?

talkEvent55_4.value: Nai thinks for a while and shakes her head very firmly to say no...

talkEvent55_5.name: Nai
talkEvent55_5.value: I am just not accustomed.....You and that person...are ...very different...to me....But I will never hate you sir...

talkEvent55_6.name: Yo
talkEvent55_6.value: I am so glad to hear such high praise from you

talkEvent55_7.name: Nai
talkEvent55_7.value: It is such a great honor to me that you are willing to keep me. How come I hate you....

talkEvent55_8.name: Yo
talkEvent55_8.value: (ah...when will she considers herself to be so low as an inferior species?

talkEvent55_9.name: Yo
talkEvent55_9.value: Not really. A girl so cute like you, there must be tons of people in this world that wish to keep you.

talkEvent55_10.value: Nai tilts her head to look at me for a while and shows somewhat surpise on her face.

talkEvent55_11.name: Nai
talkEvent55_11.value: Sir...apart from my mom, you are the first to praise me being cute.

talkEvent55_12.name: Yo
talkEvent55_12.value: It's probably because...we both love you...

talkEvent55_13.value: Nai's face turns red surprisingly and she looks away and does not dare to look at me. She just nods slightly and says--

talkEvent56_2.value: Nai looks at me as if to say something.

talkEvent56_3.name: Nai
talkEvent56_3.value: ....Sir, why are you willing to be so good to me? Encouraging me to work and study and help me find interesting things?

talkEvent56_4.name: Yo
talkEvent56_4.value: ...um, does all this need to have reasons? It's just that I want to be good to you.

talkEvent56_5.name: Nai
talkEvent56_5.value: Sir...I feel a bit flattered to hear you say so...Apart from Mom, there has never been someone thinking I am a good girl...

talkEvent56_6.name: Yo
talkEvent56_6.value: I want to be good to you and this has nothing to do with whether it is worthwhile.

talkEvent56_7.value: We should not look at things from such discriminating perspective when we do things. Sometimes, it is just that simple, willing or unwilling.

talkEvent56_8.name: Nai
talkEvent56_8.value: ...Just like you said, we should learn to reject things that we don't want to do?

talkEvent56_9.name: Yo
talkEvent56_9.value: Yes..You can understand it that way. I want to be good to you, not because you mean any values to me. It's just because I am willing to do it.

talkEvent56_10.name: Nai
talkEvent56_10.value: ....So I do not need to have any values to expect love from others...

talkEvent56_11.name: Yo
talkEvent56_11.value: Of course. If someone loves you, it's all about you and has nothing to do with anything else.

talkEvent56_12.name: Nai
talkEvent56_12.value: ...Sir, what you said makes me....a little happy...

talkEvent56_13.name: Yo
talkEvent56_13.value: Just do what you want to do and be happy. You should gradually learn to relax your real feeling in a more relaxed manner.

talkEvent57_1.name: Nai
talkEvent57_1.value: ....Sir, you are curious about my past, aren't you?

talkEvent57_2.name: Yo
talkEvent57_2.value: well, my curiosity is not devil. But Nai, are you willing to tell me?

talkEvent57_3.name: Nai
talkEvent57_3.value: ....I just want to have a try...because of what you have said...

talkEvent57_4.name: Nai
talkEvent57_4.value: The more afraid I feel, the more I need to force myself to go head. Otherwise, maybe I will never be able to confront it.

talkEvent57_5.name: Yo
talkEvent57_5.value: You are really listening to my advice. I am so happy.

talkEvent57_6.name: Nai
talkEvent57_6.value: ...I want to tell you that ....the friend that I talked about previously...

talkEvent57_8.name: Yo
talkEvent57_8.value: ...Not a person? what do you mean by that? sounds so scary...

talkEvent57_9.name: Nai
talkEvent57_9.value: ...Actually...it was just the teddy bear that I talked about before...

talkEvent57_10.name: Nai
talkEvent57_10.value: She is my only friend...I will tell all of her stories to her so she is the friend that knows about all of my secrets..

talkEvent57_12.name: Nai
talkEvent57_12.value: Because I am really afraid of being lonely...But nobody has accompanied me since Mom left...

talkEvent57_13.value: I captured one piece of information sensitively...

talkEvent57_15.name: Nai
talkEvent57_15.value: I am so lonely so the teddy bear is my best friend...

talkEvent57_16.name: Nai
talkEvent57_16.value: Sir, I am really useless, aren't I?

talkEvent57_17.value: She asks me in a timid way, which makes me heart-aching.I stroke her head to encourage her...

talkEvent57_18.name: Yo
talkEvent57_18.value: Not really. Everyone will be afraid of loneliness and I am no exception. But from now on, we will live together and will not feel afraid nor lonley with support from each other.

talkEvent58_2.value: Nai thinks about it for a long while

talkEvent58_3.name: Nai
talkEvent58_3.value: When working at a hotel, I met a family of three. It reminded me of the time to see the snow...

talkEvent58_4.name: Yo
talkEvent58_4.value: ....you meant you and your mom went to see the snow?

talkEvent58_5.name: Nai
talkEvent58_5.value: ...Yes, at that time...we live in a small hotel just like this...

talkEvent58_6.name: Yo
talkEvent58_6.value: Go on and talk more about it..

talkEvent58_7.name: Nai
talkEvent58_7.value: ...Mom embraced me in arms and fell in asleep....Although the bed in the hotel is not big, It was very warm...

talkEvent58_8.value: There was an expression of retrospect on Nai's face. She was so lost in her few beautiful memories that I feel it appropriate to interrupt her.

talkEvent59_1.name: Yo
talkEvent59_1.value: ....looking at snow at that time....that person also went?

talkEvent59_2.value: I do not miss the key information of "the family of three"

talkEvent59_4.name: Yo
talkEvent59_4.value: But that person...always liked to do some thing very abnormal?

talkEvent59_6.name: Yo
talkEvent59_6.value: But the memory back then was beautiful for you?

talkEvent59_8.name: Yo
talkEvent59_8.value: (That person had beautiful memories with Nai? I am getting more confused...)

talkEvent60_2.value: Nai keeps looking at me as if to say something.

talkEvent60_3.name: Nai
talkEvent60_3.value: ...Sir...Actually that person isn't always like that...He was once very gentle to me...

talkEvent60_5.name: Nai
talkEvent60_5.value: But....later...because of my fault, that person started to hate me, which was reasonable.

talkEvent60_6.name: Yo
talkEvent60_6.value: Nai, what are you talking about?

talkEvent60_8.value: Nai keeps silent and is reluctant to reply.

talkEvent60_9.value: I could not get more information but what's certain is that it must have to do with Nai's past.

talkEvent61_1.name: Yo
talkEvent61_1.value: Is anything new to learn in school?

talkEvent61_2.name: Nai
talkEvent61_2.value: ...Recently I went to the handicraft class...

talkEvent61_3.name: Yo
talkEvent61_3.value: Really? What did you do then?

talkEvent61_4.name: Nai
talkEvent61_4.value: ...I was not good at it. I made ugly dolls.

talkEvent61_6.name: Yo
talkEvent61_6.value: Nai, how about us making a deal?

talkEvent61_8.name: Yo
talkEvent61_8.value: You learn the handicraft well and make some handicraft product for me that you think is pretty, OK?

talkEvent61_9.name: Nai
talkEvent61_9.value: ....OK, I will work hard to learn it well...
